These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, peach, apricot, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, board-games, puzzles, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, basketball, swimming
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person eating grapes##6
 5. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
 8. the person eating peach is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
 9. the person eating strawberry is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
12. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
13. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
14. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | strawberry         | grapes     | apricot     | peach         |
| Hobby   | board-games | filmmaking    | puzzles     | photography |
| Sport   | surfing       | lacrosse | swimming | basketball       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, lemonade, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, security-guard, scientist, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, biathlon, cricket, volleyball
 1. the scientist is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person drinking cola is the security-guard##1
 5. the fisherman is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fisherman##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade          | soy-milk      | cola      | 7up   |
| Job        | scientist     | fisherman | security-guard | entrepreneur      |
| Sport      | volleyball | biathlon    | lacrosse  | cricket |

