.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, woodworking, chess, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, rock, hip-hop, reggae
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, trike, bike
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 5. the person driving the skateboard is not the fan of metal##6
 6. the fan of metal is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of reggae##8
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess  | woodworking | rock-climbing | writing |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | metal      | reggae | hip-hop        |
| Transport     | skateboard | trike       | bike    | scooter     |

