.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, romance, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, country, techno, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, turkish, malaysian, japanese
 1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 2. the turkish is not to the left of the fan of country##8
 3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the turkish##8
 6. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 8. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
 9. the dutch is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is the malaysian##1
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | disaster | sports    | romance |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | country     | gospel   | trance     |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian   | turkish | japanese    |

