.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, baking, rock-climbing, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, disaster, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, tennis, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
 8. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing       | skydiving | baking  | photography    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster       | musical    | animation | martial-arts    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball   | tennis   | rowing |

