.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cherry, lime, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, musical, superhero, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, mexican, indonesian, german
 1. the person eating lime is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 2. the person watching mystery movies is not the mexican##6
 3. the indonesian is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person watching mystery movies##7
 4. the mexican is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the indonesian is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 8. the german is between the person eating eggplant and the indonesian##2
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person eating eggplant##8
10. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
11. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | cherry      | lime      | radish | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts    | mystery | musical     |
| Nationality   | chinese    | indonesian | german  | mexican |

