 7. the person driving the scooter is not the argentine##6
 8. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the argentine##8
 9. the argentine is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
10. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
11. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the argentine##8
12. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
13. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
