.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, 7up, tea
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, raspberry, mango, broccoli
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, techno, d&b, r&b
1. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
2. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating mango##7
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
4. the fan of d&b is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the person eating zucchini is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
7. the person eating broccoli is the fan of techno##1
8. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person drinking mirinda##7
9. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | cola | 7up  | tea |
| Food          | raspberry | broccoli   | zucchini | mango |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | techno   | r&b      | d&b      |

