.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, writing, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, mexican, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bus, roller, snowmobile
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 2. the russian is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the mexican##7
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 4. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the nigerian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 7. the russian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 8. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
10. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
11. the nigerian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
13. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | writing | sudoku | card-games    |
| Nationality   | mexican  | russian    | nigerian      | italian |
| Transport     | bus | van          | snowmobile      | roller       |

