 4. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 6. the person watching crime movies is the security-guard##1
 7. the dressmaker is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 8. the security-guard is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 9. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
10. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
11. the dancer is not the person drinking fanta##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | lemonade  | fanta | cola |
| Job           | dressmaker | security-guard | engineer | dancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | crime  | drama   | martial-arts   |

