 4. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 5. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
10. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
