There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, french, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, train, scooter
 1. the australian is somewhere to the right of the french##5
 2. the fisherman is on the left of the australian##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the mechanic##1
 6. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
 7. the librarian is the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is not the mechanic##6
 9. the librarian is not to the left of the turkish##8
10. the turkish is not to the right of the mechanic##8
11. the social-worker is somewhere between the turkish and the person driving the quad-bike##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Job           | fisherman  | social-worker | mechanic | librarian |
| Nationality   | french | australian           | turkish  | russian |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | train           | scooter     | bike  |

