 7. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
10. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
11. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
12. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is camping##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
