 7. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 8. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 9. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
10. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
11. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | traveling | camping    | board-games | baking |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | punk | d&b     | jazz |
| Pet           | guinea-pig    | snake     | goat      | hamster    |

