6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the turkish##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
9. the person who's sport is cricket is the japanese##1

